pullRequest.body:
Define the equivalence between direct limits of isomorphic systems, and the equivalence between the direct limit of a system of substructures and the union of these substructures.
Co-authored-by: Aaron Anderson <awainverse@gmail.com>

---
Important additions:
- In DirectLimit:
  - Defined `Equiv_iSup`, the isomorphism between a direct limit of a system of substructures and their union.
  - Defined `equiv_lift`, the equivalence between the direct limits of two isomorphic directed systems
  
Also added some results about limits, and simple simp lemmas.
This is some preparation work for  #9967.
